Package edu.kit.scc.dem.wapsrv.app

Contains the main application that starts the Spring framework along with configuration and other common features.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CorsConfiguration
    This class centrally manages all CORS relevant configuration
    CorsFilter
    A cross origin filter that enhances the original jetty implementation
    ErrorMessageRegistry
    This class is the central registry for all error messages that should have a static message.
    EtagFactory
    This class creates ETag for usage at various points in the server.
    FusekiRunner
    Runs the Fuseki Servers as soon as the Application Context of Spring is fully started
    WapServerApplication
    Main class of the application.
    WapServerConfig
    Contains the configuration and the global constants that affect the entire application.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ConfigurationKeys
    The keys that can be used within the configuration.
